'''Abdelhazzi Kamaradimo''' (born 10 April 1984 in [[Saint-Denis, Seine-Saint-Denis|Saint-Denis]], [[Paris]]), is a [[France|French]]-born [[Mauritania]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who plays for Romanian [[Liga II]] club [[FC Farul Constanţa|Farul Constanţa]]<ref>[http://www.cugetliber.ro/1252270800/articol/47153/farul-il-are-in-probe-pe-stoperul-kamara-abdelhazzi/ Farul îl are în probe pe stoperul Kamara Abdelhazzi]</ref> and for the [[Mauritania national football team|Mauritanian national team]]. His primary position is as a left back in defence.
==International career== Kamara is a member of the [[Mauritania national football team]].<ref>{{FIFA player|297769}}</ref>
