'''Club Cristóbal Colón de Juan Augusto Saldívar''' is a [[Paraguay]]an [[Association football|football]] club based in [[Juan Augusto Saldívar]] in the [[Central Department]] of Paraguay. The club currently competes in the [[Paraguayan Cuarta División|Paraguayan Primera División C]].

