'''Delfines del Este Fútbol Club''' are a Dominican Republic professional [[association football|football]] club which competes in the [[Liga Dominicana de Fútbol]]. They are based in The club is based in [[La Romana, Dominican Republic|La Romana]]. The club was established in 2014 after the [[Dominican Football Federation]] announced the creation of a professional league, the Liga Dominicana de Fútbol.

