{{infobox country at games | NOC = SOL | NOCname = National Olympic Committee of Solomon Islands | games = Olympics | year = | flagcaption = [[Flag of the Solomon Islands]] | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.oceaniasport.com/solomon }} | location = | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = {{Team appearances list|team=Solomon Islands|competition=Summer Olympics|begin_year=1984|end_year= }} | winterappearances = | seealso = }} The '''[[Solomon Islands]]''' first participated at the '''[[Olympic Games]]''' in 1984, and has sent athletes to compete in every [[Summer Olympic Games]] since then. The nation has never participated in the [[Winter Olympic Games]].
