The '''Tour of Taihu Lake''' is a staged cycling race held in [[China]] annually in November. It has been held since 2010, but the first edition was a one-day race. The 2010 and 2011 editions were rated 1.2 and 2.2, and was upgraded to 2.1 in 2013.

[[Jakub Mareczko]] holds the record for most number of stage wins, with 15, as of the end of the 2017 edition of the race.<ref>http://www.procyclingstats.com/race.php?id=182222&c=6</ref>
